Package: sgmcmc
Type: Package
Title: Stochastic Gradient Markov Chain Monte Carlo
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: Jack Baker, Christopher Nemeth, Paul Fearnhead
Maintainer: Jack Baker <j.baker1@lancaster.ac.uk>
Description: R library for performing stochastic gradient MCMC
  including SGLD, SGHMC, SGNHT. Library is built on 'TensorFlow' 
  <https://www.tensorflow.org/>, a library for efficient numerical computation.
